== Comtitude ==

Author Antti Jaakkola (annttu(a) annttu.fi)

Description:
Simple python script to update your google latitude location 
based on information about wlans and cell-ids around computer.

Scripts user wlan mac-addresses and cell-ids from usb modem within google api 
to locate 

Dependencies:
google-api-python-client: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-python-client/downloads/list
* easy_install google-api-python-client
Pyserial
* easy_install -U pyserial
urllib2
json
libxml2

Before use you need to register a domain for oauth.

You can do it here: https://www.google.com/accounts/ManageDomains

Put your domain and customer_secret to googledata.py file
